{"tid":2264490,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"高等法院頒布「針對司法人員及其家屬被起底及滋擾」的臨時禁制令(HCA 1847/2020) 律政司：有責任捍衞法治","createTime":"2020-10-30T16:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T23:51:29.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2eb2a5f52deb83fa5dbf24231800b99fc954f5de","tid":2264490,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:14:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202010/30/P2020103001020.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202010%2F30%2FP2020103001020.htm&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdjizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=efdc0b65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202010/30/P2020103001020.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n高等法院頒布「針對司法人員及其家屬被起底及滋擾」的臨時禁制令(HCA 1847/2020)<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  自2019年6月以來，香港發生了很多公眾活動。遺憾的是，有相當數量的人訴諸暴力，以表達對政府、警察、司法人員及其他持相反觀點的人士的不滿。<br />\n   <br />\n  社會動盪也引起了一股普遍的網上文化，以「起底」攻擊與自身持相反意見的人士，及政治立場或信念與自身相衝突的人士。自2019年11月以來，警方在各種社交媒體上觀察到針對司法人員進行的「起底」活動，而這種活動在最近幾個月有所惡化。這些行為對司法人員及其家庭成員構成滋擾。<br />\n   <br />\n  律政司司長作為公眾利益守護者，以尋求維護法治和司法公正，今天向高等法院申請單方面禁制令（HCA 1847/2020&ndash;原High Court Intended Action 212/2020），以禁制任何人非法地及故意地作出以下行為：<br />\n <br />\n  (a) 在沒有相關人士的同意下及同時有意圖或相當可能會恐嚇、騷擾、威脅或煩擾相關人士的情況下使用、發佈、傳達或披露給他人屬於司法人員（如《司法人員推薦委員會條例》（第92章）第2條所定義）、暫委法官、區域法官、裁判官、審裁處法官、死因裁判官和紀錄法院各成員（以下統稱為&ldquo;司法人員&rdquo;） 及/或其配偶及/或家庭成員（即父母，子女或兄弟姐妹）的個人資料，包括但不限於他們的姓名、職位、住宅地址、辦公地址、電子郵件地址、學校地址、年齡、出生日期、電話號碼、香港身份證號碼或其他任何官方身份證明文件的號碼、Facebook帳戶ID、Instagram帳戶ID、車牌號碼和任何照片。<br />\n   <br />\n  (b) 恐嚇、騷擾、威脅或煩擾任何上述人士、及／或其配偶及／或其家庭成員。<br />\n   <br />\n  (c) 協助、造成、慫使、促致、唆使、煽動、協助、教唆或授權他人從事上述任何行為或參與上述任何行為。<br />\n <br />\n  律政司司長尋求此禁制令，以禁制這些「起底」活動。高等法院於2020年10月30日頒發臨時禁制令，有效至2020年11月13日上午10時30分。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年10月30日（星期五）<br />\n香港時間23時47分"},{"pid":"e06275f05fdf9ddd00f6e3f53e9ccf40c7cae7c0","tid":2264490,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65aed74001589041b46e1f90736747d6f18cbf0","tid":2264490,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e06275f05fdf9ddd00f6e3f53e9ccf40c7cae7c0","tid":2264490,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6340b872cd0362e8245c23597589156619a1eb21","tid":2264490,"uid":370061,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:17:10.000Z","msg":"通共狗官<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">蘇文隆</span></span>"},{"pid":"16dabd1622d5bdaa079b819e3db6126b0f3138f1","tid":2264490,"uid":379150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:17:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51118430efdb4ae6220ddec70cf04e81f8efc6e2","tid":2264490,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:17:16.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"f2f05b7866d167d8a0091f42a325d1416f4f935d","tid":2264490,"uid":80851,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:17:47.000Z","msg":"講到藍屍冇起底 冇惡意攻擊法官咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1365baf434707300332fa05596eb3af3f52fb9","tid":2264490,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d65aed74001589041b46e1f90736747d6f18cbf0","tid":2264490,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e06275f05fdf9ddd00f6e3f53e9ccf40c7cae7c0","tid":2264490,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:18:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd657bdbe6eb1d5c649521523b1ba5e55d04724","tid":2264490,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:18:32.000Z","msg":"驚紅官比美國制裁？"},{"pid":"c49471aed9d50645160970db8a29d7c07fef4b36","tid":2264490,"uid":95577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f2f05b7866d167d8a0091f42a325d1416f4f935d","tid":2264490,"uid":80851,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:17:47.000Z","msg":"講到藍屍冇起底 冇惡意攻擊法官咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:18:54.000Z","msg":"何俊堯單野斷估唔係抗爭者果邊搞掛"},{"pid":"36039c388a35b89f7b2bdbd7bf30b4d23dd8786c","tid":2264490,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6340b872cd0362e8245c23597589156619a1eb21","tid":2264490,"uid":370061,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:17:10.000Z","msg":"通共狗官<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">蘇文隆</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:18:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccad81d675d58e1496bcd82b1655be7db886e947","tid":2264490,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:19:33.000Z","msg":"以後唔講得官嘅名？"},{"pid":"28e50fb934704c5de795297e8a58b5196a24da5f","tid":2264490,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:19:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202010/30/P2020103000977.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202010%2F30%2FP2020103000977.htm&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdjizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=bf6f2d8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202010/30/P2020103000977.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n禁制令禁止對司法人員作出「起底」行為<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  高等法院原訟法庭今日（十月三十日）批准了一項臨時禁制令，以禁止對司法人員及其家庭成員進行非法和故意的「起底」行為、恐嚇、煩擾或威脅他們。臨時禁制令有效至二○二○年十一月十三日（星期五）上午十時三十分，屆時申請會於法庭再訊。<br />\n<br />\n  律政司司長作為公眾利益守護者向法庭單方面申請禁制令，以禁止任何人非法和故意地從事該等行為。<br />\n<br />\n  自二○一九年十一月起，在社交媒體平台上出現大量針對司法人員及其家屬的「起底」活動，而此等活動於近月持續出現。這些「起底」活動完全是不可接受的。<br />\n<br />\n  正如法院在最近一宗藐視法庭案件的裁決中指出，「起底」本身可構成犯罪活動。任何針對司法人員及其家屬的違法行為都不會被縱容。<br />\n<br />\n  律政司司長作為公眾利益守護者，有責任採取行動，以捍衞法治和維護司法公正。<br />\n<br />\n  任何違反臨時禁制令的人士均有可能干犯藐視法庭，並可被判處監禁或罰款。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年10月30日（星期五）<br />\n香港時間22時47分"},{"pid":"fd21fbac5c4e3b359d94bd3b58b21cc5ea462afa","tid":2264490,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef1365baf434707300332fa05596eb3af3f52fb9","tid":2264490,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d65aed74001589041b46e1f90736747d6f18cbf0","tid":2264490,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e06275f05fdf9ddd00f6e3f53e9ccf40c7cae7c0","tid":2264490,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:18:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:21:20.000Z","msg":"法庭post要你"},{"pid":"7a8aea367988edea87afb94ebe776d88e69d67aa","tid":2264490,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:21:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4204004d48bef7dfca62dd85acd5d08296b5ca2f","tid":2264490,"uid":53278,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:23:59.000Z","msg":"律政司本身就破壞緊公眾利益<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a99b0478dbf27a840a731013c6cfc2a2a8a7a0","tid":2264490,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:25:35.000Z","msg":"乜香港仲有法治去比你捍衞?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33eadbdfa7db67a7a61a7744288f55778905a4a2","tid":2264490,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd21fbac5c4e3b359d94bd3b58b21cc5ea462afa","tid":2264490,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef1365baf434707300332fa05596eb3af3f52fb9","tid":2264490,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d65aed74001589041b46e1f90736747d6f18cbf0","tid":2264490,"uid